      <prop type="x-translation-ref">采葛.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼采葛兮，一日不見，如三月兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>One day gone by, when absent from you,
Seems like three months.
I gather and dress the dolichos; —
When shall I see you again?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
